# Day 52 – System Design & Technical Blueprint

##  Overview

Day 52 focused on transforming the approved product idea into a complete technical blueprint before implementation. The goal was to finalize the architecture, API design, database schema, UI flow, and project structure so development can begin immediately without additional planning.

## Project

**PaperLens – AI-Powered Research Paper Analysis Platform**

PaperLens is an AI-powered web application designed for researchers and students to simplify literature reviews. It enables users to upload multiple research papers, generate structured summaries, compare methodologies and findings, identify research gaps, and create literature survey drafts.

##  Technical Design Completed

* System Architecture
* Database Schema
* REST API Design
* UI Flow & Wireframes
* Project Folder Structure
* Updated Implementation Blueprint

